OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill start showery. However, some
OL,7,Fclear spells are likely to develop for
OL,8,Fa time after dusk as the showers die
OL,9,Fout. Overnight, low cloud will edge
OL,10,Facross the region from the east,
OL,11,Fbringing patchy drizzle and hill fog.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FTuesday will start generally
OL,14,Fgrey with patchy drizzle and hill fog.
OL,15,FHowever, skies will gradually brighten
OL,16,Ffrom the east. Becoming sunny later.
OL,17,FFeeling cooler than Monday with an
OL,18,Feasterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
