OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FPlenty
OL,6,Fof fine weather on Wednesday and
OL,7,FThursday with some warm sunshine,
OL,8,Fthough a cooling easterly breeze
OL,9,Fblowing. More humid on Friday, with
OL,10,Flighter winds, though some showers
OL,11,Fpossible later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
